---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import Navigation from '../components/Navigation.astro';
---

<BaseLayout 
  title="Ketamine Therapy - Karen Rabins, LCSW in Raleigh, NC" 
  description="Innovative ketamine therapy for treatment-resistant depression, anxiety, PTSD, and chronic pain. Compassionate care with Karen Rabins, LCSW in a safe, clinical environment in Raleigh, NC."
  keywords="ketamine therapy Raleigh NC, treatment resistant depression, ketamine assisted therapy, PTSD treatment, anxiety therapy, innovative mental health treatment"
>
  <div slot="nav">
    <Navigation currentPage="ketamine" />
  </div>

  <!-- Hero Section -->
  <section class="relative bg-gradient-to-br from-emerald-50 to-teal-50 rounded-2xl p-8 sm:p-12 lg:p-16 mb-16">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto text-center">
      <h1 class="text-4xl sm:text-5xl lg:text-6xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-6">
        Ketamine Assisted Psychotherapy (KAP) in <span class="text-emerald-700">Raleigh, NC</span>
      </h1>
      <p class="text-xl sm:text-2xl text-gray-700 mb-8 leading-relaxed">
        As a trained Ketamine Assisted Psychotherapist, I provid specialized support during treatment. In follow-up therapy sessions I help you process your experience and insights, maintaining and building upon treatment progress. I work in collaboration with your psychiatric provider.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- What is Ketamine Therapy -->
  <section class="mb-16">
    <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-8 sm:p-12 shadow-lg border border-gray-100">
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
        <h2 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-8 text-center">What is Ketamine Therapy?</h2>
        <div class="prose prose-lg prose-emerald max-w-none">
          <p class="text-lg text-gray-700 leading-relaxed mb-6">
            Ketamine therapy is an evidenced based approach to treating mental health conditions that haven't responded to traditional treatments. Unlike conventional antidepressants that target serotonin, ketamine works on the brain's glutamate system, promoting new neural connections and offering rapid relief for many patients.
          </p>
          <p class="text-lg text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">
            The addition of Ketamine to the process of therapy can provide significant results for 55% - 70% of those challenged with treatment resistant depression. For more information about this: (Click on link to living arts)
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Conditions Treated -->
  <section class="mb-16">
    <h2 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-12 text-center">Ketamine has shown benefits for:</h2>
    
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
      <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-8 shadow-lg hover:shadow-xl transition-all duration-300 border-l-4 border-emerald-500">
        <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-emerald-100 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mb-6">
          <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-emerald-700" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
            <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zM8.707 7.293a1 1 0 00-1.414 1.414L8.586 10l-1.293 1.293a1 1 0 101.414 1.414L10 11.414l1.293 1.293a1 1 0 001.414-1.414L11.414 10l1.293-1.293a1 1 0 00-1.414-1.414L10 8.586 8.707 7.293z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-emerald-700 mb-3">Treatment-Resistant Depression</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-600">For those who haven't found relief with traditional antidepressants and therapy approaches</p>
      </div>
      
      <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-8 shadow-lg hover:shadow-xl transition-all duration-300 border-l-4 border-emerald-500">
        <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-emerald-100 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mb-6">
          <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-emerald-700" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
            <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M18 10a8 8 0 11-16 0 8 8 0 0116 0zm-7-4a1 1 0 11-2 0 1 1 0 012 0zM9 9a1 1 0 000 2v3a1 1 0 001 1h1a1 1 0 100-2v-3a1 1 0 00-1-1H9z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-emerald-700 mb-3">Severe Anxiety Disorders</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-600">Including generalized anxiety, social anxiety, and panic disorders that haven't responded to conventional treatment</p>
      </div>
      
      <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-8 shadow-lg hover:shadow-xl transition-all duration-300 border-l-4 border-emerald-500">
        <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-emerald-100 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mb-6">
          <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-emerald-700" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
            <path d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m6 2a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"></path>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-emerald-700 mb-3">Post-Traumatic Stress Disorder</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-600">Helping process and heal from traumatic experiences when traditional PTSD treatments aren't sufficient</p>
      </div>
      
      <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-8 shadow-lg hover:shadow-xl transition-all duration-300 border-l-4 border-emerald-500">
        <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-emerald-100 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mb-6">
          <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-emerald-700" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
            <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M3 6a3 3 0 013-3h10a1 1 0 01.8 1.6L14.25 8l2.55 3.4A1 1 0 0116 13H6a1 1 0 00-1 1v3a1 1 0 11-2 0V6z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-emerald-700 mb-3">Chronic Pain with Depression</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-600">Addressing both physical and emotional aspects of chronic pain conditions</p>
      </div>
      
      <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-8 shadow-lg hover:shadow-xl transition-all duration-300 border-l-4 border-emerald-500">
        <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-emerald-100 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mb-6">
          <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-emerald-700" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
            <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M18 10a8 8 0 11-16 0 8 8 0 0116 0zm-6-3a2 2 0 11-4 0 2 2 0 014 0zm-2 4a5 5 0 00-4.546 2.916A5.986 5.986 0 0010 16a5.986 5.986 0 004.546-2.084A5 5 0 0010 11z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-emerald-700 mb-3">Suicidal Ideation</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-600">Rapid intervention for acute suicidal thoughts when other treatments have failed</p>
      </div>
      
      <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-8 shadow-lg hover:shadow-xl transition-all duration-300 border-l-4 border-emerald-500">
        <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-emerald-100 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mb-6">
          <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-emerald-700" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
            <path d="M9.049 2.927c.3-.921 1.603-.921 1.902 0l1.07 3.292a1 1 0 00.95.69h3.462c.969 0 1.371 1.24.588 1.81l-2.8 2.034a1 1 0 00-.364 1.118l1.07 3.292c.3.921-.755 1.688-1.54 1.118l-2.8-2.034a1 1 0 00-1.175 0l-2.8 2.034c-.784.57-1.838-.197-1.539-1.118l1.07-3.292a1 1 0 00-.364-1.118L2.98 8.72c-.783-.57-.38-1.81.588-1.81h3.461a1 1 0 00.951-.69l1.07-3.292z"></path>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-emerald-700 mb-3">Bipolar Depression</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-600">Specialized treatment for the depressive episodes of bipolar disorder</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Treatment Process -->
  <section class="mb-16">
    <div class="bg-gradient-to-r from-emerald-50 to-teal-50 rounded-2xl p-8 sm:p-12">
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
        <h2 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-12 text-center">The KAP Treatment Process</h2>
        
        <div class="space-y-8">
          <div class="flex items-start gap-6">
            <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-emerald-200 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0">
              <span class="text-emerald-700 font-bold text-xl">1</span>
            </div>
            <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-6 shadow-lg flex-1">
              <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-emerald-700 mb-3">Initial Consultation</h3>
              <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">Comprehensive evaluation to determine if ketamine therapy is right for you, including review of your treatment history and current symptoms.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          
          <div class="flex items-start gap-6">
            <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-emerald-200 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0">
              <span class="text-emerald-700 font-bold text-xl">2</span>
            </div>
            <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-6 shadow-lg flex-1">
              <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-emerald-700 mb-3">Medical Clearance</h3>
              <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">Collaboration with an on-site psychiatric medical providers who completes a physical examination and lab work to ensure safety for treatment, including cardiovascular and mental health assessments, and determines your specific treatment protocol.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          
          <div class="flex items-start gap-6">
            <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-emerald-200 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0">
              <span class="text-emerald-700 font-bold text-xl">3</span>
            </div>
            <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-6 shadow-lg flex-1">
              <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-emerald-700 mb-3">Treatment Sessions</h3>
              <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">Carefully monitored ketamine administration in a comfortable, clinical setting with continuous professional supervision.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          
          <div class="flex items-start gap-6">
            <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-emerald-200 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0">
              <span class="text-emerald-700 font-bold text-xl">4</span>
            </div>
            <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-6 shadow-lg flex-1">
              <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-emerald-700 mb-3">Integration Therapy</h3>
              <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">Follow-up therapy sessions to process insights and experiences, maintaining and building upon treatment progress.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Safety & Monitoring -->
  <section class="mb-16">
    <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-8 sm:p-12 shadow-lg border border-gray-100">
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
        <h2 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-8 text-center">Safety & Monitoring</h2>
        <p class="text-lg text-gray-700 text-center mb-8 leading-relaxed">
          Your safety is our highest priority. All ketamine treatments are conducted in a clinical setting with comprehensive monitoring and professional oversight.
        </p>
        
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-8">
          <div class="space-y-4">
            <div class="flex items-center gap-3">
              <div class="w-8 h-8 bg-emerald-100 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center">
                <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-emerald-700" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                  <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
                </svg>
              </div>
              <span class="text-gray-700">Continuous vital sign monitoring</span>
            </div>
            
            <div class="flex items-center gap-3">
              <div class="w-8 h-8 bg-emerald-100 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center">
                <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-emerald-700" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                  <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
                </svg>
              </div>
              <span class="text-gray-700">Board-certified medical supervision</span>
            </div>
            
            <div class="flex items-center gap-3">
              <div class="w-8 h-8 bg-emerald-100 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center">
                <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-emerald-700" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                  <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
                </svg>
              </div>
              <span class="text-gray-700">Comfortable, private treatment rooms</span>
            </div>
          </div>
          
          <div class="space-y-4">
            <div class="flex items-center gap-3">
              <div class="w-8 h-8 bg-emerald-100 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center">
                <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-emerald-700" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                  <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
                </svg>
              </div>
              <span class="text-gray-700">Emergency protocols and equipment on-site</span>
            </div>
            
            <div class="flex items-center gap-3">
              <div class="w-8 h-8 bg-emerald-100 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center">
                <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-emerald-700" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                  <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
                </svg>
              </div>
              <span class="text-gray-700">Individualized dosing based on response</span>
            </div>
            
            <div class="flex items-center gap-3">
              <div class="w-8 h-8 bg-emerald-100 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center">
                <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-emerald-700" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                  <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
                </svg>
              </div>
              <span class="text-gray-700">Pre-treatment screening and assessment</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Patient Testimonial -->
  <section class="mb-16">
    <div class="bg-emerald-700 text-white rounded-2xl p-8 sm:p-12">
      <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto text-center">
        <blockquote class="text-xl sm:text-2xl italic mb-4 leading-relaxed">
          "After years of struggling with depression that didn't respond to medication, ketamine therapy gave me my life back. Karen created such a safe, supportive environment throughout the process."
        </blockquote>
        <p class="text-lg opacity-90">— Anonymous Patient</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CTA Section -->
  <section class="mb-16">
    <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-emerald-50 to-teal-50 rounded-2xl p-8 sm:p-12 text-center">
      <h2 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">Ready to Learn More?</h2>
      <p class="text-xl text-gray-700 mb-8 max-w-2xl mx-auto">If you've been struggling with treatment-resistant mental health conditions, ketamine therapy may offer new hope.</p>
      <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 justify-center items-center">
        <a href="tel:+19195787109" class="bg-emerald-700 text-white px-8 py-4 rounded-lg hover:bg-emerald-800 transition-all duration-300 hover:scale-105 shadow-lg font-semibold text-lg">
          Schedule Consultation: (919) 578-7109
        </a>
        <a href="/contact" class="text-emerald-700 hover:text-emerald-800 font-semibold text-lg">
          Learn More About Getting Started →
        </a>
      </div>
      <p class="text-sm text-gray-600 mt-6">Free 15-minute consultation • Call to discuss if ketamine therapy is right for you</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <div slot="footer" class="space-y-4">
    <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row justify-between items-center gap-4">
      <div class="text-center sm:text-left">
        <h3 class="font-bold text-gray-900 mb-1">Karen Rabins, LCSW</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-600">Licensed Clinical Social Worker • Raleigh, NC 27613</p>
      </div>
      <div class="flex gap-6">
        <a href="/" class="hover:text-emerald-700 transition-colors">Home</a>
        <a href="/about" class="hover:text-emerald-700 transition-colors">About</a>
        <a href="/services" class="hover:text-emerald-700 transition-colors">Services</a>
        <a href="/ketamine-therapy" class="hover:text-emerald-700 transition-colors">Ketamine Therapy</a>
        <a href="/contact" class="hover:text-emerald-700 transition-colors">Contact</a>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="border-t border-gray-200 pt-4">
      <p class="text-sm">&copy; 2025 Karen Rabins, LCSW. All rights reserved.</p>
      <p class="text-sm mt-1 font-medium text-emerald-700">Free 15-minute consultation available.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>